    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches, scuffs, and some paint wear beyond typical use, though there are no major structural dents. The interior has visible wear on the seats, trim, and surfaces, indicating significant prior use. Mechanically the car is functional, but buyers should expect cosmetic imperfections and potentially some deferred maintenance.",
